headline: The Iowan Who Owns 13 Ford Broncos
summary: In 1977, I was riding a bus to school and I saw a Ford Bronco for the first time.  Now so many years later, I have owned probably 35 Broncos.  Ford launched the Bronco 60 years ago this summer, and the company still makes the Bronco.
